---
title: Chorizo & Veggie Grilled Gnocchi with Sugo & Rocket-Pear Salad
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if that
hasn’t got your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-veggie-loaded-baked-gnocchi-b590b4bf.jpg
